New York State  Westchester County
http://www.westchestergov.com/health/Westnile.htm
Westchester County today postponed ground spraying plans for tonight,
Thursday, September 21, in the communities of Ardsley, Dobbs Ferry, Mt.
Pleasant, Mt. Vernon, Pleasantville, Sleepy Hollow and Tarrytown due to
anticipated cold weather.
[This is good news. If cold weather is beginning to restrict mosquito
activity in downstate New York, the days of the epidemic are numbered. 
Mod.JW
